540
01:10:45,865 --> 01:10:49,365
...and had my boy, Feilan.

541
01:10:51,907 --> 01:10:56,324
She only had a cheap little girl...

542
01:10:57,490 --> 01:11:00,240
...born three hours after my son.

543
