794
01:39:06,076 --> 01:39:09,160
I'm only repeating what they said.

795
01:39:09,618 --> 01:39:13,160
She can't blame you. It's her destiny.

796
01:39:15,993 --> 01:39:17,160
Where is she now?

797
01:39:19,785 --> 01:39:22,826
